I maintain HowmMode, and occasionally write other small garbages for fun.

; atode.el : attach alarm to any buffer (http://howm.sourceforge.jp/a/atode.el)
; iigrep.el : incremental interactive grep (http://howm.sourceforge.jp/a/iigrep.el)
; smarter-find.el : enhanced version of smart-find.el (http://howm.sourceforge.jp/a/smart-find/smart-find.el)
; snap.el : save/load snapshot of application to/from text (http://howm.sourceforge.jp/a/snap.el)
; spiral.el : write string spirally (http://howm.sourceforge.jp/a/spiral.el)
; rich-title.jl : show everything on title bar in sawfish (http://howm.sourceforge.jp/a/rich-title/)

I use Emacs. My email address is written in above *.el.

